{"word":"G4648 - σκοπέω - skopéō - skop-eh'-o - Consider","slug":"G4648","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">σκοπέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>skopéō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>skop-eh'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Consider"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03C3;&#x03BA;&#x03BF;&#x03C0;&#x03B5;&#x0301;&#x03C9; - skopeo&#x0304;</b> - <i>skop-eh'-o</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G4649\">G4649</a>; to take <i>aim</i> at (<i>spy</i>), that is, (figuratively) <i>regard:</i> - consider, take heed, look at (on), mark. Compare <a href=\"#/G3700\">G3700</a>."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G2684\">G2684</a>, <a href=\"#/G2685\">G2685</a>, <a href=\"#/G4649\">G4649</a>"}]}